oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Coldspring mountain
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white photograph of a view of Coldspring Mountain. Several houses and farm structures appear to be in the foreground in front of the mountains. It appears to have recently snowed in the area.
Made with a 5x7 aerial camera mounted on the ground.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
